# OFDM System Architecture

```text
+-------------+
| Random Bits |
+-------------+
       |
       v
+----------------+
| QPSK Modulator |
+----------------+
       |
       v
+----------------+
| OFDM (IFFT)    |
+----------------+
       |
       v
+----------------+
| Cyclic Prefix  |
+----------------+
       |
       v
+----------------+
| AWGN Channel   |
+----------------+
       |
       v
+----------------+
| Remove CP      |
+----------------+
       |
       v
+----------------+
| FFT Receiver   |
+----------------+
       |
       v
+------------------+
| QPSK Demodulator |
+------------------+
       |
       v
+----------------+
| BER Analysis   |
+----------------+
```

